"repositories\"/>)."
msgstr ""
"Installare il pacchetto <application>audacity </application> dal repository "
"<emphasis>Universe</emphasis> (vedere <xref linkend=\"extra-"
"repositories\"/>)."

#: C/common-tasks.xml:149(para)
msgid ""
"To run <application>Audacity</application>, choose <menuchoice><guimenu>K-"
"Menu</guimenu>\n"
"                            <guisubmenu>Multimedia</guisubmenu>\n"
"                            <guimenuitem>Audacity</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Per far eseguire <application>Audacity</application>, selezionare "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Menu K</guimenu>\n"
"                             <guisubmenu>Multimedia</guisubmenu>\n"
"                             "
"<guimenuitem>Audacity</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#: C/common-tasks.xml:158(para)
msgid ""
"For further help about using Audacity, consult the program's help by "
