"                             <guisubmenu>Contents</guisubmenu></menuchoice>."

#: C/common-tasks.xml:169(title)
msgid "Video"
msgstr "Video"

#: C/common-tasks.xml:170(para)
msgid ""
"Many video formats can be played in Kubuntu using free codecs found in the "
"repositories. This includes formats such as MPEG and other common video "
"formats. To install further codec support see <xref linkend=\"codecs\"/>."
msgstr ""
"Molti formati video possono essere letti da Kubuntu, usando i codec liberi "
"nei repository. Questo include formati come gli MPEG ed altri formati video "
"comuni. Per installare il supporto per ulteriori codec vedere <xref "
"linkend=\"codecs\"/>."

#: C/common-tasks.xml:171(para)
msgid ""
"In Kubuntu, videos can be played with the "
"<application>Kaffeine</application> Media Player. Some features of "
"<application>Kaffeine</application> include custom playlists, DVD playback "
"and more. You can start <application>Kaffeine</application> by clicking: "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>K-Menu</guimenu>\n"
"                <guisubmenu>Multimedia</guisubmenu>\n"
"                <guimenuitem>Kaffeine (Media "
"Player)</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"In Kubuntu, i video possono essere riprodotti col Media Player "
"<application>Kaffeine</application>. Alcune funzionalità di "
"<application>Kaffeine</application> includono la creazione di playlist "
"personalizzate, riproduzione di DVD ed altro ancora. Si può avviare "
"<application>Kaffeine</application> facendo clic su: "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Menu K</guimenu>\n"
"                 <guisubmenu>Multimedia</guisubmenu>\n"
"                 <guimenuitem>Kaffeine (Media "
"Player)</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#: C/common-tasks.xml:182(title)
msgid "DVD Playback"
msgstr "Riproduzione di DVD"

#: C/common-tasks.xml:183(para)
msgid ""
"The legal status of this library is not fully clear. In some countries it is "
"possible that the use of this library to play or copy DVDs is not permitted "
"by law. Verify that you are within your rights in using it."
msgstr ""
